OL,3,CGuernsey charities call for exemption
OL,4,Cfrom goods and service tax
OL,6,FA lack of increased funding over the
OL,7,Fpast decade has seen Guernsey
OL,8,Fcharities cut services and go out of
OL,9,Fbusiness due to rising running costs,
OL,10,Fthe Association of Guernsey Charities
OL,11,Fclaim.
OL,13,FThe States of Guernsey have around #5
OL,14,Fmillion for 30 separate funding
OL,15,Farrangements with island charities,
OL,16,Fbut there has been little increase to
OL,17,Fthis funding since it was first
OL,18,Fringfenced in 2014.
