OL,3,CGuernsey charities call for exemption
OL,4,Cfrom goods and service tax
OL,6,FCharities are concerned that
OL,7,Fintroducing a goods and services tax
OL,8,F(GST) on top of rising costs could
OL,9,Fshutter their charitable endeavours.
OL,11,FThe Mill Street Community Cafe has
OL,12,Fprovided an essential service for
OL,13,Fyears, but say the increasing cost of
OL,14,Fliving and the possibility of GST are
OL,15,Fthreatening its survival.
OL,17,FDavid Savident, the cafe's Accounts
OL,18,FManager, explains: "We'd have to
OL,19,Fdecide whether we need to increase our
OL,20,Fprices and that has a knock-on effect
OL,21,Fon the customers that come here.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
