OL,3,CGuernsey charities call for exemption
OL,4,Cfrom goods and service tax
OL,6,FCurrently, charities in Jersey, the
OL,7,FIsle of Man, and the UK are exempt
OL,8,Ffrom GST, but Wayne Bulpitt, the Chair
OL,9,Fof the Association of Guernsey
OL,10,FCharities, says there is still no
OL,11,Fconsistency as to how much charities
OL,12,Fget from the States.
OL,14,FHe explains: "We had a social compact
OL,15,Fwith the States at Guernsey in 2014,
OL,16,Fand it really has not been delivered
OL,17,Fon.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
