OL,6,FMr Bulpitt suggests: "We believe
OL,7,Faround #100 million of unclaimed
OL,8,Fdividends, dormant bank accounts,
OL,9,Fseized assets, and similar, but our
OL,10,Fisland has been very slow in releasing
OL,11,Fthose funds for charitable purposes.
OL,13,F"The UK, Jersey, the Isle of Man, all
OL,14,Fhave schemes to release them. We
OL,15,Fbelieve that just the interest of that
OL,16,Fwould be a significant boost to our
OL,17,Fsector employees."
