OL,3,CGuernsey charities call for exemption
OL,4,Cfrom goods and service tax
OL,6,F"In the third sector, you've got great
OL,7,Fskilled people, lots of potential, and
OL,8,Fefficient organisations, but how do
OL,9,Fyou release that for the benefit of
OL,10,FGuernsey?
OL,12,F"Just like politicians, people working
OL,13,Fin charities are passionate about what
OL,14,Fthey do, and they want to make the
OL,15,Fisland a better place for everyone.
OL,17,F"If we can release (financial)
OL,18,Fresources, then maybe we can deliver a
OL,19,Fmore efficient island and deliver
OL,20,Fgrowth."
