OL,3,CGuernsey charities call for exemption
OL,4,Cfrom goods and service tax
OL,6,FMr Steele spoke to election candidates
OL,7,Flast week and urged them to work with
OL,8,Fcharities and deliver stable financial
OL,9,Fbacking, rather than through
OL,10,Finconsistent grants.
OL,12,FHe concludes: "Treat us as equal
OL,13,Fpartners; don't just dump stuff or
OL,14,Fexpect the third sector to deliver for
OL,15,Ffree. Treat us with professionalism."
